LOT NO. 2, CCS-11-000807

A PARCEL OF LAND (LOT 2, Ccs-11-000807, consolidation and subdivision of Block 42, 43 and 44, Ts-229-D) situated in Barangay Poblacion, Municipality of Padada, Province of Davao del Sur, Island of Mindanao. Bounded on the N., along lines 14-1 by Lot 1; on the E., along lines 1-2 by Lot 4; both if Ccs-11-000807; on the S., along lines 2-3-4-5-6-7-8-9-10; on the W., along lines 10-11-12-13-14 both by Road.

Beginning at a point marked “1” on Plan, being S. 77 deg. 12′ W., 1,949.42 m from BLLM No. 134, Cad-275, thence:

The parcels of land herein reserved shall be non-alienable and shall not be subject to occupation, entry, sale or lease, or other mode of disposition until again declared alienable by the President through the issuance of proclamation.beginning, containing an area of EIGHT THOUSAND TWO HUNDRED NINE (8,209) SQUARE METERS , more or less, Corner 2 is “GS” Cyl. Con. Mons. 15 x 60 cm. and the rest are “Old Points”. Bearings true. Date of original survey, April 14 to May 12, 1952; Date of Subdivision Survey, February 1, 2001 executed by Geodetic Engineer Isidro P. Guarra and approved on May 28, 2001.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 26th day of May , in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Four.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

